dct_description_sm: Shows built up areas, roads, railway, important places, and buildings. "Government of Pākistān copyright reserved." Area surveyed 1985-86. "REG. No. 427 RWD '89 ..." "Refer to this map as 1:25,000 Hyderabad guide map first edition." "List of names and history of Hyderābād printed on reverse."
